reviews.author: Tony Travels
reviews.content: I've been using Cannabis in all it's forms for 30 years plus. I went to Sawasdee for chronic pain and inflammation from old sports injuries, insomnia and anxiety. I had been to multiple other clinics in Thailand before - Phuket, Pattaya and Bangkok - so my expectations were low. Other Clinic's products were either crudely produced and overpriced (600% more than Sawasdee at one place) or they were Pharma Grade but Isolates and not a Full-Spectrum (natural) extract and STILL overpriced 4-500% compared with Sawasdee. Regardless, I was blown away by the quality and potency of Sawasdee's oil. I would like to try other products now. Price was also amazing, extremely reasonable. Best products at the best price in my experience but I've only tried their extracts/tinctures/oils. Definitely worth your time.
